<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink344">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>naṟumpūṅ kuravam payanta</l>
<l>ceyyāp pāvai koyyum poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived,  </l>
<l>when unmade dolls yielded by fragrant  </l>
<l>blooming bottle-flower trees, are plucked.  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
